    <article>

      <p><strong>Hi</strong>, hello, as all these great minicomics are making their way to people's mailboxes across the world, we wanted to take a moment and spread some love to some people that didn't get a chance to subscribe this year, so:</p>
      <p>Every couple of months we'll be <strong>giving away</strong> a comic to someone who isn't a subscriber yet. Sign up for our mailing list and we'll <strong>draw out</strong> a name and send out our first three minicomics. </p>
      <div id="subscribe">{{> mailchimp}}</div>
      <p>
        <img src="img/{{ asset 'this.month.jpg' }}"/>
      </p>
      <p>This month we have <strong>Matt Emery's</strong> <em>Mere &amp; Mary</em>, <strong>Tom Eccles's</strong> <em>Yoink</em> and <strong>Ashley Ronning's</strong> <em>Closest Approach</em> - send us your email by 31st January and you could have all three of these finding their way to your mailbox!</p>
      <p>We'll also send you a nice risograph poster that <a href="http://heliopress.bigcartel.com/">Ashley</a> made for us.</p>
      
      <div class="callout">
        <p>Do you know someone else who would be into this? We'd love it if you told them about it, or shared us around on <a class="fb-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/minicomic.club/">Facebook</a> or <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A//smallercomics.com/minicomics-of-the-month/2015/january.html&via=smallercomics&text=Minicomics!">Twitter</a></p>
      </div>
    </article>
    
    {{>footer}}
